2. 

In this Order— 

“Act of 2007” means the Water Services Act 2007 (No. 30 of 2007); 

“accessories” has the meaning assigned to it by the Act of 2007; 

“dwelling” has the meaning assigned to it by section 4 of the Affordable 
Housing Act 2021 (No. 25 of 2021); 

“housing estate” means a group of dwellings built together as a single 
development; 

“land” has the meaning assigned to it by the Act of 2007; 

“pipe” has the meaning assigned to it by the Act of 2007; 

“sewer” has the meaning assigned to it by the Act of 2007; 

“storm water sewer” has the meaning assigned to it by the Act of 2007; 

“water main” has the meaning assigned to it by the Act of 2007; 

“water services authority” has the meaning assigned to it by the Act of 2007.
